videos.headline: Feaster spins out of a tackle and runs for a South Carolina TD
videos.description: South Carolina RB Tavien Feaster avoids a would-be tackler with a spin move and goes 34 yards for a Gamecocks' touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Feaster spins out of a tackle and runs for a South Carolina TD) 2019/08/31

videos.headline: South Carolina gets great field position off 60-yard kickoff return
videos.description: South Carolina's Shi Smith gets the Gamecocks in North Carolina territory after returning the kickoff 60 yards.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (South Carolina gets great field position off 60-yard kickoff return) 2019/08/31

videos.headline: Bentley makes UNC pay for poor coverage with TD
videos.description: South Carolina QB Jake Bentley hits a wide-open Kyle Markway in the middle of the field for a Gamecocks touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (South Carolina makes UNC pay for poor coverage with TD) 2019/08/31

videos.headline: UNC QB coughs up the football
videos.description: North Carolina QB Sam Howell tries to escape the rush and loses the ball, giving the ball to South Carolina solid field position.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UNC QB coughs up the football) 2019/08/31

videos.headline: UNC's Brown makes excellent juggling TD grab
videos.description: Sam Howell lofts up the fade and Dyami Brown bobbles the ball and hauls it in for the 22-yard score.

videos.headline: UNC comes all the way back with Corrales' TD catch
videos.description: Beau Corrales makes the difficult touchdown grab for North Carolina to give them the lead after trailing by as many as 11.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UNC comes all the way back with Corrales' TD catch) 2019/08/31

videos.headline: UNC all but locks up win with INT
videos.description: Jake Bentley throws an interception to North Carolina's Myles Wolfolk which halts the Gamecocks' drive down the field.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UNC all but locks up win with INT) 2019/08/31
